'''天主教恩多拉教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Ndolaënsis}}；{{lang-en|Diocese of Ndola}}）是[[贊比亞|贊比亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教盧薩卡總教區|盧薩卡總教區]]。

教區的前身是一個於1938年1月8日成立的宗座監牧區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=V |year=1938 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=277-278 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-30-1938-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703121316/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-30-1938-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-07-03 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1949年1月13日升為宗座代牧區，1959年4月25日升為教區<ref>{{cite web |title=RHODESIAE SEPTEMTRIONALIS ET NYASSALAND* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-xxiii/la/apost_constitutions/1959/documents/hf_j-xxiii_apc_19590425_rhodesiae.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703113358/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-xxiii/la/apost_constitutions/1959/documents/hf_j-xxiii_apc_19590425_rhodesiae.html |archivedate=2020-07-03 |language=la |date=1959-04-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區位於[[銅帶省|銅帶省]]，2004年有850,000名教友（佔轄區總人口42.5%）、69個[[堂區|堂區]]和98名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-de|本雅明·菲里|Benjamin Phiri}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 03.07.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/03/200703a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703111251/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/03/200703a.html |archivedate=2020-07-03 |language=en |date=2020-07-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|諾埃爾·嘉祿·奧里根|Noel Charles O’Regan}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 16.01.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/01/16/0031/00060.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703115541/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/01/16/0031/00060.html |archivedate=2020-07-03 |language=it |date=2010-01-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

